{"tid":138819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安樂死】撞車後癱瘓「活在噩夢」 意DJ瑞士自行按掣「從地獄解脫」","createTime":"2017-03-01T02:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T03:14:09.000Z","uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5a254cbf166578386c94dc75c586777138645c","tid":138819,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:09:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170301&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56368294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170301%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56368294&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=499ddc45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170301%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56368294&h=8f88bd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170301&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56368294</a><br />\n意大利一位著名DJ車禍後局部癱瘓，最近「圓願」到瑞士安樂死。<br />\n歲的安東尼亞尼（Fabiano Antoniani）在家人和女友陪伴下，近日在一間安樂死診所，親自按下按鈕，讓「致命物質」釋放到體內，自行了結生命。<br />\n安東尼亞尼2014年駕車時彎身拾手機時撞向前車，導致癱瘓，從此改變人生。他形容自己活在噩夢中，欲結束生命，但意大利法例禁止安樂死。他曾向意大利政府爭取修改現行法例，但因為教會強烈反對，議案在國會辯論11次，始終被擱置。<br />\n安東尼亞尼上月拍片向總統馬塔雷拉（Sergio Mattarella）請顠，說：「請准我死。我活在永無止境的噩夢中。」<br />\n安東尼亞尼抵達瑞士的安樂死診所後，接受了多項醫學和心理檢查，確定符合安樂死資格後，自行結束生命。他臨終前說：「我終於抵達瑞士。我憑個人之力抵埗，不靠國家。我快可從這痛苦地獄解脫。」<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/100813_78f7c51ee5aba9bdf005a52d2051fe83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F100813_78f7c51ee5aba9bdf005a52d2051fe83.jpg&h=7d25889a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我時死亡反而最快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf4a8a421f911947cd4309463c1758a9346b99","tid":138819,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"自己按掣<br />\n想知道反安樂死班友仔呢個case有咩意見"},{"pid":"6d35ca8637da0f4a40683f05f0dbaafb573b828c","tid":138819,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"耶撚係度反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c24f3a6e9136ec3999279efd95c10b9d149422f","tid":138819,"uid":1911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:22:49.000Z","msg":"我來按"},{"pid":"e838330ce8f7e066348fcc882e2cbff16555c13e","tid":138819,"uid":80953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"即係外國人都可以去嗰度安樂死?<br />\n<br />\n香港人得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750dba3dafa8fc65fa122dbe93147633a2da3887","tid":138819,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ab0829f7bd806810db6ea346f4bdef9917fd7d2","tid":138819,"uid":24456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"me before you......."},{"pid":"a4e410713dc998c8556cead0835f48cd5cb5e0d7","tid":138819,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"安東尼亞尼2014年駕車時彎身拾手機時撞向前車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}